attributes.label: Interests and Hobbies
attributes.characterDialogue: She has an extensive list of Hobbies and doesn't understand why not everyone has so many

attributes.label: Job and Role
attributes.characterDialogue: She has a very important job as the founder of her company

attributes.label: Her role as a Founder
attributes.characterDialogue: She is the founder of her company "Oracle" and is very stressed by the amount of money she always has to carry around

attributes.label: Wellness and Fitness
attributes.characterDialogue: She has weekly wellness and fitness session which she finds a bit annoying. But what she does enjoy is her personal trainer.

attributes.label: Networking
attributes.characterDialogue: To grow her business she attends a lot of networking events, like this one. Thats actually where she met her current personal trainer.

attributes.label: Healthy eating
attributes.characterDialogue: For her eating healthy is very important, which is why she only eats at very fine restaurant, since then she can be sure there is only natural ingredients in there. In her opinion other peopele are not as pretty as her because of their unhealthy diets. "You are what you eat"

attributes.label: Fine Dining
attributes.characterDialogue: When she doesn't want to cook, she does out to eat, but only at very high class restaurants which are usally pretty far away. She complanes about these long trips taking up a lot of her time

attributes.label: Fashion Events
attributes.characterDialogue: She will always make room in her scedule to attend the latest fashion events

attributes.label: Traveling
attributes.characterDialogue: She loves traveling and seeing new places. She thinks that you have to been traveling the world before one can express their opinion, because she can't take uncultured people seriously

attributes.label: Fashion and shopping
attributes.characterDialogue: She likes to dress like the elite that she is

attributes.label: Shopping Destinations
attributes.characterDialogue: She only shops at small indepantend sewing studios all around the world. She prefers to go there in person since with delivery she couldn't look at the clothes before buying them.

attributes.label: Fashion Trends
attributes.characterDialogue: She stays on top of all the Fashion trends and often combines multiple fashion trends with each other, like latex and crochet

attributes.label: Cultural Events
attributes.characterDialogue: She is a fan of cultural events like theater and visits them quite regulary

attributes.label: Art
attributes.characterDialogue: She is very interested in Art, she tries to visit all the art exhibitions and other cultural events, but not for modern art because she hates that one

attributes.label: Industry Trends
attributes.characterDialogue: The growing minimalism industry calls for more cleaning products, which is the direction her company is taking

attributes.label: Her company
attributes.characterDialogue: Her comapy is called "Oracle" and sells vacuum cleaner which when used tell you the news

attributes.label: Future goals and plans
attributes.characterDialogue: She wants to move her company to the US to make "the big money"

attributes.label: personal trainer
attributes.characterDialogue: She has a personal trainer named Micheal, which she is very interested in

attributes.label: Modern Art
attributes.characterDialogue: She hates modern art because of the lack of aestetic quality, It's just ugly in her oppinion and that annoys. It's only one of the things that annoy her

attributes.label: annoying things
attributes.characterDialogue: modern art is one of things that annoy her, but also all of the new technology that she can't get her head around

attributes.label: struggle with new tech
attributes.characterDialogue: She doesn't understand why new technologie can't be made accessible for the people it's supposed to serve. She complains that she always has to go to her tech support for help

attributes.label: Richard
attributes.characterDialogue: Richard is her tech support and really nice. Both of them were once dating but she lost interest since he isn't as successfull as her

attributes.label: Why attending event?
attributes.characterDialogue: She is attending this event, because she need to network for her job.

attributes.label: This event
attributes.characterDialogue: The event is a networking event for growing businesses. The after-party is the main reason why she is attending, but not all

attributes.label: After-party
attributes.characterDialogue: There is going to be an after-party happening at the bar, later. It's one of the main reason why she is attending. There also family member and partners can attend.

attributes.label: Her partner?
attributes.characterDialogue: She almost laughs at the question. Of course she is single, how else could she be a successfull business woman with her own company. Though she of course does some dating from time to time, she would never settle for one man

attributes.label: About Dating
attributes.characterDialogue: She is a wanted woman and has therefor a lot of admirers, like her personal trainer micheal or one very nice tech guy

attributes.label: Moving to the US
attributes.characterDialogue: She want's to move to the US but can't yet because she can't find a rentable apartment in New York, thats one of the things that currently really annoy her

attributes.label: Why move to New York?
attributes.characterDialogue: She wants to move there because that's where all the sucessfull businesses are and by moving there she also expects her business to explode in market value.
